        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "When should I use ultra-budget builders?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Use Hostinger ($2.99), Zyro ($3), Webnode ($4) when: testing a business idea, building temporary site, learning web design, absolute budget constraint (can't afford $9/mo). Don't use when: professional business site, e-commerce, serious brand, long-term project, need good SEO. Budget builders are for experiments, not businesses. If you're serious about your site, start at $9/mo. The $6 difference prevents 10x headaches later."
